These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, gardening
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, engineer
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, indie
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, volleyball
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, may
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the accountant##1
4. the person who likes blood-red is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |
| Beverage      | sprite     | hot-chocolate |
| Hobby         | gardening  | camping       |
| Job           | engineer   | accountant    |
| Color   | blood-red     | lavender   |
| Music-Genre   | indie      | classical     |
| Sport         | volleyball | swimming      |
| Birthday     | may       | august           |

