.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, water
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, salsa
City: edinburgh, hannover
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, zombie
2 different pets are kept: hamster, horse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, rowing
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, snowmobile
1. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3
5. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Beverage      | water       | coffee     |
| Music-Genre         | salsa | classical    |
| City           | hannover   | edinburgh |
| Movie-Genre   | musical     | zombie     |
| Pet           | hamster     | horse      |
| Sport         | cycling     | rowing     |
| Transport     | snowmobile  | car        |

